{"title":"英雄联盟RiotGame客户端设置中文","uid":"ba262b3a30ea998ca4c88f2720f764bc","slug":"英雄联盟RiotGame客户端设置中文","date":"2021-11-30T19:26:19.581Z","updated":"2021-12-01T03:07:28.286Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/英雄联盟RiotGame客户端设置中文.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>受够了TX的嘴脸，一堆恶心人的强制手段，虽然说我从小到大基本玩的就是腾讯代理的游戏，单单英雄联盟都玩了十年，但我热爱的是游戏本身跟你TX没半毛钱关系。同一台电脑，玩TX服帧数不到六十，换外服基本在一百多左右，这客户端到底是塞了多少东西</p></blockquote>\n<p>我转到了最近的日服，因为TW服的模式和TX也差不多，客户端也是塞了不少东西，于是我直接选了官方亚洲的服务器，日服。</p>\n<p>换到官方服务器切切实实感受到了什么是简约并且好用，UI 又漂亮，并且云顶之弈客户端和手游的数据是互通的，TX硬生生又给拆开了，解决掉语言问题我应该就一直玩外服了。</p>\n<p>中文教程：找到 <code>C:\\ProgramData\\Riot Games\\Metadata\\league_of_legends.live</code> 路径下的 <code>league_of_legends.live.product_settings.yaml</code> 文件，将里面的 <code>en_US</code> ，或者是 <code>ja_JP</code> 修改为 <code>zh_CN</code> ，然后重启游戏，等待更新完毕即可转成中文。</p>\n<p><strong>注意：这样会造成客户端首页的内容丢失，但并不影响游戏的体验，想要恢复就改回来就行。</strong></p>\n","feature":"trues","text":" 受够了TX的嘴脸，一堆恶心人的强制手段，虽然说我从小到大基本玩的就是腾讯代理的游戏，单单英雄联盟都玩了十年，但我热爱的是游戏本身跟你TX没半毛钱关系。同一台电脑，玩TX服帧数不到六十，换外服基本在一百多左右，这客户端到底是塞了多少东西 我转到了最近的日服，因为TW服的模式和TX...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":482,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Game","slug":"Game","count":1,"path":"api/categories/Game.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"League of Legends","slug":"League-of-Legends","count":1,"path":"api/tags/League-of-Legends.json"}],"toc":"","author":{"name":"Reticentar","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/12/01/o8SvSf.png","link":"/","description":"想做的太多，时间却太少","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/Reticentar","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{},"next_post":{"title":"修复WSL2子系统安装宝塔无法打开面板问题","uid":"1475960420406d5ca85c990dc97bd9b5","slug":"修复WSL2子系统无法联网问题","date":"2021-11-29T18:02:52.290Z","updated":"2021-11-29T19:55:03.949Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/修复WSL2子系统无法联网问题.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":" 因为想在 WIN11 本地通过 WSL2 的子系统安装宝塔进行网站搭建，但是遇到了一个很头疼的问题，就是宝塔是安装了，却无法进入宝塔，搜寻了一遍没有解决方案，最后看到一篇文章找到了解决办法 一开始我就猜想是不是因为 WSL2 子系统的端口被限制，所以导致无法通过端口打开宝塔面板...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":661,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Develop","slug":"Develop","count":6,"path":"api/categories/Develop.json